      "content": "activism? like, what's the point of fighting for a tiny bit of time when the math is just against us? it feels like trying to fix a leaking boat while the ocean is literally swallowing it. i just feel so exhausted by the futility of it all. like, why should i even bother staying around to watch the end?",
